some object ids are not in the client.java…
like danger signs. you have to use the deleteobject method.

i suggest if you cannot find it, use the method or you could be here for a long time.

it also doesnt really matter how big the client.java is because only you will have it unless you release but i doubt you would do that when your trying to get rid of shit.
